
### Additional substitution keys  
* __CLIENT_TOTAL_REMISE_DISPO__                 => available customer discounts (credit notes or deposits)
* __CLIENT_TOTAL_AVOIR_DISPO__                  => available credit notes
* __CLIENT_TOTAL_FACTURE_IMPAYEE__              => amount outstanding
* __CLIENT_TOTAL_FACTURE_IMPAYEE_ONLY_POS__     => positive outstanding amount (if amount is negative, display 0)

Other possibilities with the current object
* __OBJECT_[ATTRIBUTE_NAME]__                   => replace [ATTRIBUTE_NAME] with the attribute name (in uppercase) of the object you wish to display (example with the ref attribute: __OBJECT_REF__).

### Hidden configuration
* GRAPEFRUIT_SUBSTITUTION_USE_CURRENCY_SYMBOL   => display currency symbol instead of spelling it out
